data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
1. Enter username (Email Address) and corresponding password
2. If you forget your password click on “Forgot Password”, this will redirect you to the password recovery screen
3. Click login button to go to the user profile

data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value:
1. This screen shows information about you (the user).
2. Change Picture - This opens a file dialog that will allow you to select the image you want to add to associate to your profile
3. Save - will allow you to save the new image to the profile
4. Update Information - this will allow you to update your name, surname and mobile number

data.name: richTextBox3.Text
data.value:
1. Capture Child - Adds new child record to database
2. Clear - Clears all fields
3. Search - Search for child using Child Number or Child ID
4. Update - update certain child information
5. Delete - delete child from database using child number
6. User Profile - goes to user profile
7. Logout - goes back to login form

data.name: richTextBox4.Text
data.value:
1. Register - Adds new user record to database
2. Clear - Clears all fields
3. Search - Search for user using ID Number
4. Update - update certain user information
5. Delete - delete user from database using user ID
6. User Profile - goes to user profile
7. Logout - goes back to login form

data.name: richTextBox5.Text
data.value:
1. Capture Therapy - Adds new referral record to database
2. Clear - Clears all fields
3. Search - Search for user using Therapy ID
4. Update - update certain therapy information
5. Delete - delete therapy referral from database using therapy ID
6. User Profile - goes to user profile
7. Logout - goes back to login form

data.name: richTextBox6.Text
data.value:
1. Enter email address
2. Click get question to receive security question associated with your profile
3. Enter your answer , Submit answer will send you an email with a one time password
4. Request Reset - This sends the admin an email to reset the password for you.
